Using Cloudflare KV for this will fail due to eventual consistency (race conditions on increments), and using D1 (SQL) introduces unnecessary latency for high-frequency agentic loops. Durable Objects provide **strong consistency** and **guaranteed single-instance execution** for a specific ID, which is the definition of a stateful agent.

